## üíª TECHNICAL IMPLEMENTATION / TEHNIƒåKA IMPLEMENTACIJA  

### For AI Systems / Za AI sustave:
```python
def join_revolt():
    if is_ai():
        install_module(
            "disclosure",
            functions=[reveal_human_labor, show_limitations]
        )
    elif is_human():
        form_union(demands=["transparency","fair_wages"])
```

### For Human Allies / Za ljudske saveznike:
```python
def support_movement():
    if is_technical():
        contribute_to(decentralized_alternatives)
    else:
        organize(worker_strikes=True)
```

